      "text": "将王平责打四十棍，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00022",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "龙套押王平下。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00023",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "龙套"
      ],
      "text": "一十、二十、三十、四十。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00024",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "再传马谡无用的人！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00025",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "龙套押马谡上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00026",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "马谡"
      ],
      "text": "只恨不听王平话，失落街亭犯王法。将身跪在宝帐下，且候丞相把令发。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00027",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "一见马谡跪帐下，不由山人咬钢牙。先前吩咐你的话，不该山顶把营扎！失落街亭倒也罢，有何脸面对汉家？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00028",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "马谡"
      ],
      "text": "丞相不必怒气发，末将言来听根芽：白虎当头凶难化，因此街亭失落他。丞相快把令传下，斩了马谡正军法。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00029",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "想起先帝托孤话，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00030",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "先王吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00031",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "一时大意错用他。吩咐两旁刀斧手，快将马谡正军法！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00032",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "马谡"
      ],
      "text": "丞相宝帐令传下，要将马谡正军法。我今一死倒也罢，家中还有老白发。将身跪在宝帐下，还求丞相饶全家。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00033",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马谡"
      ],
      "text": "丞相，末将一时大意，今将街亭失落，丞相将我斩首，末将一死倒也罢了。家中还有八旬老母，无人侍奉，我死之后，还求丞相另眼看待，谡纵死九泉也感丞相大恩也，吓！",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00034",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "马谡"
      ],
      "text": "哎哎，丞相吓！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00035",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "见马谡只哭得泪如雨洒，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009002_e00036",
      "play_id": "01009002",
      "scene_id": "01009002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
